imdb.plot outline: Two Spy Sisters, trained in espionage and combat by their Secret Agent Adopted Father, go deep undercover as party bimbo Co-Presidents of the Alpha Delta Pi sorority. Their mission: Protect their mad scientist, little sister and her future-tech gadgets from falling into the wrong hands while keeping their spy-lives secret from her and their sorority sisters.
imdb.title: The Sisters Classified
